{"tid":408601,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"今日個天好靚 有無人睇到","createTime":"2017-09-21T10:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T11:17:28.000Z","uid":38552,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ed20cf979baca978b844179a4cfd34ac4397779","tid":408601,"uid":38552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T10:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/185942_c3be54614c46ab35a371389ab41e82a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F185942_c3be54614c46ab35a371389ab41e82a2.jpg&h=803eaf1d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/21/185945_7441a1279d02f869215b1b43c8b72bbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F21%2F185945_7441a1279d02f869215b1b43c8b72bbc.jpg&h=c9b92322&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0b82393d262847e2d0b1921e59f48c09a932009","tid":408601,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:07:25.000Z","msg":"東九制高點？"},{"pid":"5ebddd7b0943b22f81b56637abbe611172c71fdc","tid":408601,"uid":38552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:09:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東九制高點？</blockquote><br />\n安達邨位置"},{"pid":"6e66307454ddf9aaccc087bfab23f9cd65c4d40c","tid":408601,"uid":63450,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T11:17:34.000Z","msg":"屌喇媽 公屋仔個景仲靚過我屋企個景"},{"pid":"1234b21c475b5fdafee6d6f5aaf385fef22715f2","tid":408601,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:19:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌喇媽 公屋仔個景仲靚過我屋企個景</blockquote><br />\n東九安達臣山日後會有私樓<br />\n到時私樓先享有制高點<br />\n你儲定銀彈啦<br />\n<br />\n08年林鄭夾硬批九西啟德地起公屋<br />\n而家啟德海邊咪又係私樓<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 啟德啟晴邨於2016年立法會選舉屬九西選區<br />\n劉游決定勝票源"},{"pid":"6a984d6d56fdc05c9d35aabe7508d8690ad0e6d6","tid":408601,"uid":38552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:28:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌喇媽 公屋仔個景仲靚過我屋企個景</blockquote><br />\n公屋黎講呢個景真係無得輸,如果住高層向海個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拍得住好多偽豪宒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c6e9fda5b039bdc31a018080592644989d561b","tid":408601,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌喇媽 公屋仔個景仲靚過我屋企個景</blockquote><br />\n公屋黎講呢個景真係無得輸,如果住高層向海個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拍得住好多偽豪宒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，但好似未入伙，而家入伙果堆好似近另一邊<br />\n<br />\n暫時最好都係曉麗苑高層"},{"pid":"64cb621ea65393f88ebf90d2f34996e042a15299","tid":408601,"uid":38552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:50:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌喇媽 公屋仔個景仲靚過我屋企個景</blockquote><br />\n公屋黎講呢個景真係無得輸,如果住高層向海個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拍得住好多偽豪宒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，但好似未入伙，而家入伙果堆好似近另一邊<br />\n<br />\n暫時最好都係曉麗苑高層</blockquote><br />\n安達北邨個影都 好正,始於位於高位 對住香港<br />\n其實成個 安達都好正,除左去MTR 比較麻煩,<br />\n去MK 尖沙咀 沙田果邊都好方便"},{"pid":"76cf5a30ab4551bb4fe0d6f3aa6166a19f3d13e3","tid":408601,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T12:52:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌喇媽 公屋仔個景仲靚過我屋企個景</blockquote><br />\n公屋黎講呢個景真係無得輸,如果住高層向海個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拍得住好多偽豪宒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，但好似未入伙，而家入伙果堆好似近另